                        <li>I read books about the structure \ architecture, different programming languages (mostly PHP), and text-markup languages</li>
                        <li>I watched all kinds of video tutorials to learn PHP, HTML and CSS</li>
                        <li>Strengthens the theory in practice learned to code, and then in all learned going to code</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr />

